  "body": "Related to #225 \r\n\r\nGeth developer chain can be run with command `--dev.period 0` in order to only mine blocks when transactions are pending.\r\n\r\nIt would be a great feature for geth clique to allow this behavior in private networks.\r\nFor example with the following setting in the genesis block:\r\n`\r\nconfig: { \r\n  { \"clique\": \r\n    \"period\": 0 }\r\n}\r\n`",
